usage: ead_tag_use.py [-h] [-outfile [OUTFILE]] dir [dir ...]

analyze EAD tag useage

positional arguments:
  dir                 EAD XML corpus directory

optional arguments:
  -h, --help          show this help message and exit
  -outfile [OUTFILE]  output tag useage report

recursively searches "*.xml" files in given dirs for EAD tags

Sample output: 
    https://gist.github.com/1614098

Dependencies: 
    lxml

Acknowledgements: 
    inspired by the tag analysis work of Kathy Wisser from Simmons.
